3. Clear Form Fields
Objective: Create a form with multiple input fields (e.g., name, email, and message). 
Add a "Clear" button that, when clicked, clears all input fields.

Steps:
Create an HTML form with input fields for name, email, and a textarea for the message.
Add a "Clear" button next to the submit button.
Attach an event listener to the "Clear" button that clears the values of all input 
fields when clicked.  